      "content": "that's a good start. can you make it a bit more descriptive about the people he's seeing? like, he should talk about how they look and their lifestyle compared to europeans, to really show why he thinks they need this \"civilizing\" mission. make it sound like a true 19th century view of them being more primitive or unrefined.",
